Jane Wall (ma bí efu ódò 1972) í chí enefu actress íya kí bí ñwu chí Nigerian kpaí atta ñwu ye chí enefu .[1] í chí ene keju ma nyo nyo ojí ye í portrayal of Constable Di Worrell efu ITV's The Bill kwí ẹgba f1999 tí 2002.[2][3]

Wall has also appeared in Dangerfield, A Touch of Frost, Doctors and Holby City.[4]

In 2014, Wall appeared in LA Theatre Works' production of Racing Demon.[5]Éwn malábó:Verification needed
